Xbox just put their brand on a handheld for the very first time, but this ROG Xbox Ally isn't quite what you'd expect. After getting hands-on time with Microsoft's new "Xbox Full Screen Experience," I'm honestly not sure if this counts as a real Xbox handheld...and the software situation is more complicated than they're letting on.
